  http://coyotegulch.scottrobertladd.net/products/evocosm/

Canonical download:
  http://coyotegulch.scottrobertladd.net/products/evocosm/libevocosm-4.0.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libevocosm-4.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libevocosm-4.0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libevocosm-4.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevocosm-4.0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevocosm4.0_4-4.0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevocosm-devel-4.0.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

